title: Freddie Gibbs joins the show!
description:
Freddie Gibbs hops on the show to preview his upcoming project "$oul $old $eparately" - as well as his love for the Bulls, his budding acting career, Jalen's golf swing, and the time Giannis flexed on his whole city. Also, he's got a list of his 5 favorite actors that you have to hear! Plus, the guys dig into the Broncos embarrassing loss in what was supposed to be Russel Wilson's revenge game. A 64 yard field goal!? All that and more.
